Yesterday's late night baking.⁣
Mini Keto Buns.⁣
No more hollow hollow ✌️. ⁣
(They looked ugly after baking but I kept them all in a ziplock bag and store inside the fridge with the baking paper. Maybe bcoz of the moisture in the fridge, it usually look nicer after taking out from fridge.) ⁣
⛔⛔⛔⛔⛔⛔⛔⛔⛔⛔⛔⛔⛔⛔
🖲️Tap on the bottom right to save📌 this recipe
⁣🖲️❤️ if you like this recipe & ▶️ to share this recipe with others. ⁣⁣
⁣
⁣⁣
⁣⁣ Ingredients: ⁣⁣
🥯⁣ 120g almond flour ⁣
🥯 0.5 tsp coconut flour ⁣
🥯 1. 5 tbsp psyllium husk ⁣
🥯 2 tsp baking powder ⁣
🥯 1 cup hot water ⁣
🥯 3 egg whites (slightly whip with pinch of salt) ⁣
🥯 2 tsp apple cider vinegar⁣
⁣
⁣
Instructions:⁣
➡️ Mix everything with a mixer.⁣
➡️ Then transfer to blender or food processor. ⁣
➡️Split into 10 portion⁣
➡️Preheat the oven at 170 degrees for 10 minutes and bake for 35 minutes. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
